# dub-cli — environment

# ============================================================
# Recommended: one Kyma key for transcription + translation
# ============================================================
# Opens the speech-to-text and translation gates through a single
# gateway with unified billing. Free credit at signup.
# Get yours at https://kymaapi.com (60-second signup, no card).
# ============================================================
KYMA_API_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Voice (text-to-speech)
# ============================================================
# Best quality uses ElevenLabs v3 directly. Set this for the natural,
# expressive voice. Without it, TTS routes through Kyma.
# ============================================================
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Optional: bring-your-own STT key (advanced fallback)
# ============================================================
# If KYMA_API_KEY is missing, transcription can run via Groq.
# (Translation still needs KYMA_API_KEY today.)
# ============================================================
# GROQ_API_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Optional overrides
# ============================================================
# DUB_KYMA_BASE=https://api.kymaapi.com
